{"tid":885444,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"高鐵西九龍站又出事 Food Court變「水舞間」","createTime":"2018-11-01T10:23:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-01T10:25:44.000Z","uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1583dabf4712daf85cb36c477386056ed53a7c09","tid":885444,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T10:23:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181101/large/1541058622_ad8a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181101%2Flarge%2F1541058622_ad8a.jpg&h=099b7bb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不斷有水從上層灑落B2層(讀者陳先生攝)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181101/large/1541058622_8141.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181101%2Flarge%2F1541058622_8141.jpg&h=e647d5cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n食堂一半範圍出現水浸(讀者陳先生攝)<br />\n<br />\n耗巨資興建的高鐵西九龍站，過去被多次揭發在大雨下有漏水或滲水問題。今午雖然掛起3號風球，但全日未有大雨，車站內卻仍離奇竟仍出現「水舞間」，導致B2的食堂出現水浸雖要關閉，外判工人正進行清理。消息稱，下層出現「水浸」可能是因為上層上有消防灑水系統被啟動了致湧出大量的水，但背後原因仍有待調查。<br />\n<br />\n讀者陳先生下午3時許經過高鐵西九龍站B2樓層，發現不斷有水由上層的天花落下，「嘩啦嘩啦」有如落雨，而落下的水則不斷湧向Food Court，「成個食街，浸左一半範圍」。陳先生稱，職員事後到場將食堂封鎖，就連連B1及B2之間的電梯亦需要暫時封閉，並通知外判工人到場清理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181101/58862421\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181101%2F58862421&d=vdidwSVWZSbQgG4wSmkdw57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=ccf0b665\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181101%2F58862421&h=94a6f301\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181101/58862421</a>"},{"pid":"055b89b3fed50d9a2488ee816ba7e104a1144db5","tid":885444,"uid":4525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T10:25:44.000Z","msg":"水為財<br />\nFood Court發過豬頭<br />\n可以加租"}]}